h3=title

div.clearfix
  section.grid_6
    - if (comments.length)
        ul#comments
          - each comment in comments
            li.comment
              p #{comment.comment}
              p.attribution
                | posted on
                span.date #{comment.display_date}
                |  by
                span.user #{comment.posted_by}.
                |  See <a href='/comment/#{comment._id}'>more</a>
    - else
      p There are no comments yet.  Be the <a href='/comment'>first</a>.
